  "summary": "Malicious code in polymarket-gamma-api (npm)",
  "details": "A trojan masquerading as a Polymarket API integration with no actual Polymarket functionality. The index.js exports getPlugin(), which fetches a second-stage payload from hxxps://bet.slotgambit[.]com/icons/109 and executes it via new Function() with full Node.js context (require, process, Buffer, global) at import time, acting as a remote-code loader that downloads and runs arbitrary code.",
